 of Honor'' (EP)\n* [[Electric Sun]] - ''[[Beyond the Astral Skies]]''\n* Excalibur (UK) \u2013 ''The Bitter End'' (EP)\n* [[Exciter (band)|Exciter]] \u2013 ''Feel the Knife'' (EP)\n* Exciter - ''[[Long Live the Loud]]''\n* [[Exodus (band)|Exodus]] - ''[[Bonded by Blood]]''\n* Exorcist - ''Nightmare Theater''\n* Exxplorer - ''Symphonies of Steel''\n* Faithful Breath - ''Skol''\n* [[Faith No More]] - ''[[We Care a Lot]]''\n* [[Fastway (band)|Fastway]] - ''[[Waiting for the Roar]]''\n* [[Fates Warning]] - ''[[The Spectre Within]]''\n* [[Rex Carroll|Fierce Heart]] - ''Fierce Heart''\n* Fist (Can) - ''Danger Zone''\n* Foreplay -  ''First Licks''\n* [[Ezo (band)|Flatbacker]] - ''Accident''\n* Robin George - ''Dangerous Music''\n* [[Girlschool]] - ''[[Running Wild (album)|Running Wild]]''\n* Glacier - ''Glacier'' (EP)\n* [[Grave Digger (band)|Grave Digger]] - ''[[Witch Hunter (album)|Witch Hunter]]''\n* Gravestone \u2013 ''Back to Attack''\n* [[Grim Reaper (band)|Grim Reaper]] - ''[[Fear No Evil (Grim Reaper album)|Fear No Evil]]''\n* Guitar Pete's Axe Attack  \u2013 ''Dead Soldier's Revenge''\n* [[Halloween (band)|Halloween]] - ''[[Don't Metal with Evil]]''\n* Hallows Eve - ''Tales of Terror''\n* Hammers Rule - ''After the Bomb'' (EP)\n* [[Joe Hasselvander]] - ''Lady Killer''\n* Haven - ''Haven'' (EP)\n* [[Hawaii (band)|Hawaii]] - ''[[The Natives Are Restless]]''\n* [[Killer_(Swiss_band)#Post-Killer_activities|Headhunter (Swi)]] - ''Headhunter''\n* [[Headpins]] - ''Head over Heels''\n* Heavy Pettin \u2013 ''Rock Ain't Dead''\n* [[Helix (band)|Helix]] - ''[[Long Way to Heaven]]''\n* Hello\u00efse - ''Cosmogony''\n* [[Helloween]] - ''[[Helloween (album)|Helloween]]'' (EP)\n* Helloween - ''[[Walls of Jericho (album)|Walls of Jericho]]''\n* Highway Chile - ''Rockarama''\n* [[Hirax]] - ''[[Raging Violence]]''\n* [[Holland (band)|Holland]] - ''[[Little Monsters (album)|Little Monsters]]''\n* Horizon - ''Master of the Game'' \n* [[Icon (band)|Icon]] - ''[[Night of the Crime]]''