ors\u00fcre \u2013 ''Acceleration Process''\n* [[M\u00f6tley Cr\u00fce]] - ''[[Theatre of Pain]]''\n* [[Nasty Savage]] - ''Nasty Savage''\n* Nightmare \u2013 ''Power of the Universe''\n* [[Nightwing (band)|Nightwing]] \u2013 ''A Night of Mystery - Alive! Alive!'' (live)\n* [[Ob\u00fas]] - ''Pega con fuerza''\n* Odin - ''Don't Take No... For an Answer'' (EP)\n* [[Omen (band)|Omen]] - ''[[Warning of Danger]]''\n* [[Overkill (band)|Overkill]] - ''[[Feel the Fire (Overkill album)|Feel the Fire]]''\n* Overkill (CA) - ''Triumph of the Will''\n* [[Onslaught (band)|Onslaught]] - ''[[Power from Hell (Onslaught album)|Power from Hell]]''\n* [[Ostrogoth (band)|Ostrogoth]] - ''Too Hot''\n* Pandemonium - ''Hole in the Sky''\n* [[Paganini (band)|Paganini]] - ''Weapon of Love''\n* [[Pantera]] - ''[[I Am the Night (album)|I Am the Night]]''\n* Paradoxx - ''Plan of Attak'' (EP)\n* [[Pentagram (band)|Pentagram (US)]] - ''[[Relentless (Pentagram album)|Pentagram]]'', aka ''Relentless''\n* [[Jack Starr|Phantom Lord]] - ''Phantom Lord''\n* [[Piledriver (band)|Piledriver]] - ''Metal Inquisition''\n* [[Possessed (band)|Possessed]] - ''[[Seven Churches (album)|Seven Churches]]''\n* [[Janet Robin#Precious Metal|Precious Metal]] - ''Right Here, Right Now''\n* [[Rail (band)|Rail]] - ''III'' \n* Railway - ''Railway II''\n* Ran \u2013 ''Burning''\n* [[Ratt]] - ''[[Invasion of Your Privacy]]''\n* [[Raven (British band)|Raven]] - ''[[Stay Hard]]''\n* [[Razor (band)|Razor]] - ''[[Executioner's Song (album)|Executioner's Song]]''\n* Razor - ''[[Evil Invaders]]''\n* [[Quiet Riot (1977 album)|Kelle Rhoads]] - ''Cheap Talkin' Romance'' (EP)\n* [[Rogue Male (band)|Rogue Male]] - ''First Visit''\n* [[Hellion_(band)#Ann Boleyn reforms Hellion with new members|Romeo]] - ''Rocks'' (EP)\n* [[Rogue Male (band)|Rogue Male]] \u2013 ''First Visit''\n* Rosy Vista - ''You Better Believe It'' (EP)\n* [[David Lee Roth]] - ''[[Crazy from the Heat]]'' (EP)\n* [[Rough Cutt]] - ''[[Rough Cutt (album)|Rough Cutt]]''\n* 